1. introduce
    This is a simple reinforcement learning implemented in c++.

2. development environment
    Ubuntu 16.04
    gcc 5.4.0

3. dependent libraries
    ncurses : for FlappyBird display
    sudo apt-get install ncurses-dev

4. compile and run
    make
    ./flappy_bird

5. note
    3 hours can reach 3000 score.
